22:49.951 --> 22:51.854
How is she,
by the way?

22:52.788 --> 22:55.155
She's okay.
She got sick last week.

22:55.157 --> 22:56.455
I know.

22:56.457 --> 22:57.859
You said.

22:59.461 --> 23:01.293
She's okay,
though, right?

23:01.295 --> 23:05.200
Yeah. You know.
Lily's Lily.

23:06.368 --> 23:08.233
Well, she's not that bad.

23:08.235 --> 23:09.402
Oh, come on.

23:09.404 --> 23:10.270
She's not like my parents.

23:10.272 --> 23:12.374
