in the world.

24:20.140 --> 24:22.075
<i>Now, things did get
out of hand</i>

24:22.077 --> 24:23.242
<i>and she lost control,</i>

24:23.244 --> 24:27.816
<i>but greed was
the original motivator.</i>

24:30.349 --> 24:33.289
