of her husband's diagnosis.

24:34.289 --> 24:37.326
James recently updated his will
to include his children.

24:37.626 --> 24:40.092
<i>For Detective Walker
and the rest of the officers</i>

24:40.094 --> 24:41.360
<i>on the Pollack case,</i>

24:41.362 --> 24:45.063
