seemed like an airtight motive.</i>

24:45.065 --> 24:48.300
<i>But some didn't believe
Casey's motivation</i>

24:48.302 --> 24:50.472
<i>was quite so simple.</i>

24:51.171 --> 24:52.571
<i>Up next...</i>

24:52.573 --> 24:55.040
<i>We sit down with one of the
only people who's heard</i>

24:55.042 --> 24:58.310
<i>Casey Pollack speak since
the traumatizing events.</i>

24:58.312 --> 25:01.417
Right here on Inside Crime.

25:11.959 --> 25:14.559
I'm not ashamed to admit
I have values.

25:14.561 --> 25:17.297
