She could kill you.

26:24.532 --> 26:26.499
I just don't want
her to worry.

26:26.501 --> 26:27.466
She's old.

26:27.468 --> 26:29.537
Oh, come on.
What are you talking about?

26:30.371 --> 26:33.005
You're like the best
good girl I know.

26:33.007 --> 26:34.741
