29:35.723 --> 29:38.624
I'm just saying
it's not unheard of to...

29:38.626 --> 29:41.694
see things out there
in the dark night.

29:41.696 --> 29:43.432
Mom!

29:44.498 --> 29:46.734
Sorry.
You're too easy.

29:57.411 --> 29:58.743
